Subject: Re: [VB] Tell me 'bout this brake hone thing

It's a device you spin on your drill that has small 'stones' on it that
are used to slightly grind the inside of a cylinder.  Your local auto
parts store should have them.

John Baker wrote:
> I have gotten some responses about reaming the swing lever pin with a "brake hone".  Can someone please tell e what this thing is and how it works?
